{{> menu}}

<section class="ui left aligned middle aligned segment">
  <div id="textPhoto">
    <div id="whiteText"><h2>{{title}}</h2></div>
    <div id="titleImg"><img src="/photos/textPhoto_FerBromHata.png"></div>
  </div>
  <h2>FerBromHata: Pioneering modern farm infrastructure through green innovation</h2>
  <p>
    FerBromHata combines decades of structural expertise with cutting-edge renewable energy and automation—helping global farmers modernize their operations while prioritizing sustainability, animal welfare, and workforce stability.
  </p>
  <div id="textPhoto">
    <img src="/photos/textPhoto_QA.png">
    <div>
      <h2>How does FerBromHata transform traditional farms into future-ready habitats?</h2>
      <p>By integrating "Green Solutions" like wind and solar power with advanced structural upgrades, FerBromHata allows farmsteads to modernize without the need for full reconstruction. Our focus remains on enhancing efficiency and animal welfare through seamless, sustainable infrastructure that adapts to the needs of the modern producer.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div id="adventages">
    <div id="iconText">
      <img src="/icons/automation.png">
      <h3>Automation</h3>
      <p>From automatic harvesting and soil testing to robotic milk collection, our software-driven systems accelerate operations while ensuring the least loss of workplaces through smart integration.</p>
    </div>
    <div id="iconText">
      <img src="/icons/scale.png">
      <h3>Scale & Reach</h3>
      <p>With a team of 1,000+ experts and 5,000+ units of proprietary equipment, we support agricultural hubs across Dublin, Limerick, Waterford, and 20 additional counties.</p>
    </div>
    <div id="iconText">
      <img src="/icons/heritage.png">
      <h3>Heritage</h3>
      <p>Founded in 1947, we have evolved from a machinery manufacturer into a green energy leader, backed by the UCD Robotics Department and government-funded innovation.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div id="textPhoto">
    <div>
      <h2>FerBromHata Solutions Directory</h2>
      <p>Connect with the advanced technologies designed to modernize your operations—from automated livestock care and waste management to green-energy-powered harvesting systems.</p>
      <button><a href="/catalog">Search now!</a></button>
    </div>
    <img src="/photos/textPhoto_search.png">
  </div>
  <h2>Cultivating a global future of ethical and efficient agriculture</h2>
  <p>FerBromHata is committed to expanding into international markets, replacing hazardous labor practices with efficient automation, and protecting livestock from environmental harm. Our mission is to increase farm income and improve agronomic culture while facilitating a safer, more productive work environment for staff worldwide.</p>
  <div id="contact">
    <div id="signUp">
      <img src="/icons/email.png">
      <h2>Sign up to our newsletter</h2>
      <input type="email" placeholder="example@example.com"></input>
      <button>Subscribe</button>
    </div>
    <a href="{{info.company.phone}}">{{info.company.phone}}</a><br>
    <a href="{{info.company.email}}">{{info.company.email}}</a><br>
    <a href="{{info.company.address}}">{{info.company.address}}</a>
  </div>
</section>

